nodes.text: Club Penguin Star Wars Rebels Takeover

Club Penguin Star Wars Rebels Takeover was an event within Disney's children's MMO, Club Penguin. It began on January 22 and ended on February 4, 2015. The event was initially announced on November 26, 2014 on ClubPenguin.com.

Players had to complete tasks to earn exclusive items, completing all tasks of the event unlocked a lightsaber, players with a membership could receive the lightsaber, wielding it, they could duel against other players wielding a lightsaber and challenge The Inquisitor to a lightsaber duel to earn more exclusive items.
